{"tid":1884401,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人home office到有小小鬱悶","createTime":"2020-02-17T14:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T11:26:52.000Z","uid":101907,"like":41,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"3481d922a11acd779ea47441490c4b7a3cb1c307","tid":1884401,"uid":101907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"新年之後一直home office<br />\n一直謹守屋企 最多落樓下買個外賣<br />\n星期一至五訓到830起身番工 <br />\n放工就跟youtube做下運動或瑜珈<br />\n每日慳左兩個鐘交通時間用嚟睇書<br />\n星期六日都係睇下書 、執下屋就一日<br />\n今年至睇左8本書 上年成年都無睇咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始頭兩星期好感激公司安排 好享受多左咁多時間<br />\n但而家差不多成個月，無出過去無社交生活搞到有小小鬱悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nhome office嘅大家多出嚟嘅時間用嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e19fb0032501938ed31d82541ec8c28d3e3724","tid":1884401,"uid":130177,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"我都好想有呢個煩惱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c247de5e6aeaf959292e1130d99ef5215b437500","tid":1884401,"uid":249263,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:47:27.000Z","msg":"上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n議員日日鬧爆支共無人理<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=f89ee9e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"6554c50a23ebb3fce2396b